{
  "stem": "6966.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when the governor wasn't looking, I had enough chocolate now and then.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, after a few weeks, I didn't like the way my hair was full of white powder when I got home in the evenings, and I had enough chocolate, so I went.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I got a job in a factory where they made wooden legs and wooden-- wooden tables.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At the very beginning-- beginning with, I arrived at 8:00 in the morning, and the governor wasn't up yet.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But-- and he left me at quarter past eight, and I had to move blocks of wood from out of the garden, which was behind the factory.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's only a little shop.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the assistant came in, and I was busy with taking the blocks of wood from out of the garden into the-- inside where the machine was.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the governor said, here are my shoes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Clean my shoes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he gave me his shoes to clean.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now these were shiny, patent shoes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I got a duster and took all the sawdust off.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they were really spotless.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I put them down and continued with my blocks of wood.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then the governor called me and he said, did you clean my shoes?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I gave him the shoes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He looked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, if I tell you to clean the shoes, you use shoe polish.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said, there was no need to clean it with shoe polish.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They're beautiful clean.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He said, you do what I tell you to do, and otherwise, you go.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I said, well I didn't come here to have an argument about cleaning your shoes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I've come here to learn the trade, so I better go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I took my hat and my coat, and I went.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
